ðŸ”— Additional Resources
For reference, you can explore the following GitHub repositories that implement similar Speech Emotion Recognition systems:

billy-enrizky/Speech-Emotion-Recognition: This project focuses on real-time SER using the RAVDESS dataset and LSTM networks.

pdadial/Speech_Emotion_Recognition_CNN-LSTM: Implements emotion recognition using a combination of CNN and LSTM networks on the RAVDESS dataset.

souradeepdutta/Speech-Emotion-Recognition-with-CNN-LSTM-CLSTM: Achieves high accuracy by combining CNN, LSTM, and CLSTM architectures across multiple datasets, including RAVDESS.
